# Our Team 

The Developer Experience team is made up of two squads, the Developer Portal Team and the Engineering Platform Team. 

## Developer Portal Team

Our mission is to make development simple and efficient so teams can focus on creating high‑quality solutions, not navigating complexity. Through continuous improvement, strong partnerships, and a deep understanding of developer needs, we aim to deliver a portal that brings visibility and alignment to engineering teams across the organisation.

## Engineering Platform Team

The Engineering Platform team will deliver the foundational tools, services, and standards that empower engineers to build, ship, and operate software with greater speed, reliability, and confidence. We are here to reduce the barrier to entry for new services by delivering automated 'Golden Paths'. 
